News Releases, Media Advisories

September 4, 2003

ATTENTION WIRE SERVICES, DAYBOOK EDITORS:
FINAL AUDIT REPORT ON
TIM BISHOP FOR CONGRESS
The Federal Election Commission has made available the final audit report on Tim Bishop for Congress (NY 1st District). This audit covers the period of March 25, 2002 through December 31, 2002.

Contact: FEC Press Office (202) 694-1220, 999 E Street, NW
title: Final Audit Report on Tim Bishop for Congress is Available
